                <div>
                    <h3>Kayaking</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Calm, crystal-blue waters of Moffat Bay</li>
                        <li>Explore quiet shorelines and hidden coves</li>
                        <li>Opportunities to see seals, eagles, and marine wildlife</li>
                        <li>Guided tours available for beginners and experienced paddlers</li>
